# 📦 Novel Office – Custom WordPress Theme

This is a fully custom-built WordPress theme for **labskillpro**, a professional software and web development company. The theme was developed as part of a web developer project assignment. It includes custom design implementation, responsiveness, performance optimizations, and WordPress best practices.

---

## 📋 Features

- ✅ Custom home-page template (`Home`)
- ✅ Fully responsive and mobile-friendly layout
- ✅ Bootstrap 5 integrated via CDN
- ✅ Custom CSS & JS enqueued properly
- ✅ Custom hero section, services, testimonials, and contact form
- ✅ Animated counters and carousel
- ✅ SEO-friendly meta setup
- ✅ Reusable structure with clean and modular code
- ✅ Performance best practices: lazy loading, minified assets
- ✅ Ready-to-extend with Custom Post Types (like Testimonials)

---

