│ ├── css/ all style here
│ └── js/ all logical part here 
├── template/ home-page.php
├── header.php
├── footer.php
├── 
├── functions.php // all css js file and menu add here 
├── index.php
├── page.php
├── style.css
├── screenshot.png  / this is the temp screenshot for side you can change 
└── README.md


## 🛠️ Installation Steps

1. Clone or download this repo.
2. Copy the theme folder (`novel-office-theme`) into your `/wp-content/themes/` directory.
3. Log in to your WordPress dashboard.
4. Go to **Appearance → Themes** and activate **labskillpro** theme.
5. Set the homepage to use the `Home` template in **Settings → Reading**.



## 🛠️ For lazy image 
The loading="lazy" attribute is used in an <img> tag to delay loading the image until it comes into view on the screen. This improves page speed and performance, especially when you have many images.


<img src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/assets/images/icon12.png" alt="Description" loading="lazy">


📈 Performance Benefits
Improves Google PageSpeed score

Helps with SEO and user experience

Great for mobile users and slow internet connections